Problem Statement 10 (Aggregation & Indexing)
Create the Collection Movies_Data( Movie_ID, Movie_Name, Director, Genre, BoxOfficeCollection) and solve the following:
1.	Display a list stating how many Movies are directed by each “Director”.
2.	Display list of Movies with the highest BoxOfficeCollection in each Genre.
3.	Display list of Movies with the highest BoxOfficeCollection in each Genre in ascending order of BoxOfficeCollection.
4.	Create an index on field Movie_ID.
5.	Create an index on fields ” Movie_Name” and ” Director”.
6.	Drop an index on field Movie_ID.
7.	Drop an index on fields ” Movie_Name” and ” Director”.
 

// =========================================
// DBMS Practical 10
// AGGREGATION & INDEXING USING MONGODB
// =========================================

// =========================================
// Step 1 : Create Database
// =========================================

use MoviesDB

// =========================================
// Step 2 : Create Collection and
// Insert Documents
// =========================================

db.Movies_Data.insertMany([

{
Movie_ID:1,
Movie_Name:"KGF",
Director:"Prashanth Neel",
Genre:"Action",
BoxOfficeCollection:1200
},

{
Movie_ID:2,
Movie_Name:"Dangal",
Director:"Nitesh Tiwari",
Genre:"Drama",
BoxOfficeCollection:2000
},

{
Movie_ID:3,
Movie_Name:"Bahubali",
Director:"S S Rajamouli",
Genre:"Action",
BoxOfficeCollection:1800
},

{
Movie_ID:4,
Movie_Name:"3 Idiots",
Director:"Rajkumar Hirani",
Genre:"Comedy",
BoxOfficeCollection:900
},

{
Movie_ID:5,
Movie_Name:"PK",
Director:"Rajkumar Hirani",
Genre:"Comedy",
BoxOfficeCollection:1200
},

{
Movie_ID:6,
Movie_Name:"RRR",
Director:"S S Rajamouli",
Genre:"Action",
BoxOfficeCollection:1500
},

{
Movie_ID:7,
Movie_Name:"Chhichhore",
Director:"Nitesh Tiwari",
Genre:"Drama",
BoxOfficeCollection:700
}

])

// =========================================
// Query 1
// Count Movies directed by each Director
// =========================================

db.Movies_Data.aggregate([

{
$group:{
_id:"$Director",
Total_Movies:{$sum:1}
}
}

])

// =========================================
// Query 2
// Highest BoxOfficeCollection in each Genre
// =========================================

db.Movies_Data.aggregate([

{
$sort:{BoxOfficeCollection:-1}
},

{
$group:{
_id:"$Genre",
Movie_Name:{$first:"$Movie_Name"},
Highest_Collection:{$first:"$BoxOfficeCollection"}
}
}

])

// =========================================
// Query 3
// Highest BoxOfficeCollection in each Genre
// in Ascending Order
// =========================================

db.Movies_Data.aggregate([

{
$sort:{BoxOfficeCollection:-1}
},

{
$group:{
_id:"$Genre",
Movie_Name:{$first:"$Movie_Name"},
Highest_Collection:{$first:"$BoxOfficeCollection"}
}
},

{
$sort:{Highest_Collection:1}
}

])

// =========================================
// Query 4
// Create Index on Movie_ID
// =========================================

db.Movies_Data.createIndex(
{
Movie_ID:1
}
)

// =========================================
// Query 5
// Create Compound Index on
// Movie_Name and Director
// =========================================

db.Movies_Data.createIndex(
{
Movie_Name:1,
Director:1
}
)

// =========================================
// Query 6
// Drop Index on Movie_ID
// =========================================

db.Movies_Data.dropIndex(
{
Movie_ID:1
}
)

// =========================================
// Query 7
// Drop Compound Index
// Movie_Name and Director
// =========================================

db.Movies_Data.dropIndex(
{
Movie_Name:1,
Director:1
}
)

